Edge EDM: Best Of 2013

                            Trance | Edge EDM Records

              320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2013-12-26 | 01:44:43 | 214 Mb


After one year of existence we are proud to say that Edge has turned into a platform for new exciting talents and rising stars. With consistent support from Armin van Buuren on A State of Trance, Edge isn't only known for its big artists, but also for serving quality sounds from undiscovered producers. A selection of 12 tracks can be found on the "Edge - Best of 2013" pack in order highlight what Edge has been about during this wonderful year. You can find tracks from Photographer, Harmonic Rush, Reorder, Ian Standerwick, Vlind, Kaimo K, Allan Morrow, and many more! Enjoy this year's overview!
